com.robopupu.api.binding

Class ViewBinding<T_View extends android.view.View>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.robopupu.api.binding.ViewBinding<T_View>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.view.View.OnClickListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AdapterViewBinding, TextViewBinding

    public abstract class ViewBinding<T_View extends android.view.View>
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.view.View.OnClickListener
    ViewBinding provides an abstract base class for objects that establish bindings from UI widgets (View instances) to other objects, such as Presenters.
